<li>I am so sorry for the loss of your wonderful daughter. My heart goes out to you.</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you during this immensely difficult time.</li>
<li>I'll always remember her kindness and warm smile.</li>
<li>She will be deeply missed by everyone who knew her.</li>
<li>Remember the joy and laughter she brought into our lives.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need, whenever you need it.</li>
<li>Your strength and resilience inspire me.</li>
<li>Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Please let me know if there's anything at all I can do to help.</li>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss; words cannot express how heartbroken I am for you.</li>
<li>Sending you all my love and support.</li>
